Acres Club.formatted_address: 411-B, Hemu Kalani Marg, Sindhi Society, Chembur East, Mumbai 400071, India
Acres Club.name: Acres Club
Acres Club.description: The Acres Club opened in 2000 in Chembur and quickly became one of the area’s finest lifestyle clubs. It offers a wide range of sports amenities including a pool, courts for tennis, badminton, squash, a football turf, table tennis and a gym, along with dining and event venues. The club serves over 2,000 members and is part of the Apurva Natvar Parikh Group.

Andheri Recreation Club.formatted_address: Dadabhai Road, Opp. Bhavan's College, Andheri (West), Mumbai 400058, India
Andheri Recreation Club.name: Andheri Recreation Club
Andheri Recreation Club.description: Founded in 1970, the Andheri Recreation Club in Andheri West offers members a blend of luxury and comprehensive sports facilities. The club features a swimming pool, lawn tennis and squash courts, badminton and table tennis areas, as well as a modern gym and health club. It is a strictly vegetarian club with banquet halls, a restaurant, guest rooms, and other amenities.

Bombay Gymkhana.formatted_address: Mahatma Gandhi Road, Fort, Mumbai 400001, India
Bombay Gymkhana.name: Bombay Gymkhana
Bombay Gymkhana.description: Established in 1875, Bombay Gymkhana is one of Mumbai’s premier private clubs. It offers facilities for rugby, football, cricket, swimming, tennis, badminton, squash, and a fitness centre. It hosted India’s first Test cricket match in 1933 and continues to be an exclusive club with a rich sporting heritage.

Bombay Presidency Golf Club.formatted_address: Dr. Choitram Gidwani Road, Chembur, Mumbai 400074, India
Bombay Presidency Golf Club.name: Bombay Presidency Golf Club
Bombay Presidency Golf Club.description: The Bombay Presidency Golf Club (BPGC) is one of the oldest and most famous golf clubs in Mumbai. Established in 1927, it features an 18-hole Par-70 course, clubhouse, dining, swimming pool, and fitness amenities. It serves as a hub for Mumbai’s golf community.

Bombay Presidency Radio Club.formatted_address: 157, Arthur Bunder Road, Colaba, Mumbai 400005, India
Bombay Presidency Radio Club.name: Bombay Presidency Radio Club
Bombay Presidency Radio Club.description: Established in 1928, Radio Club offers a sea-facing pool, indoor sports, and a health club near the Gateway of India. It blends vintage charm with modern recreation for its private members.

Breach Candy Swimming & Bath Trust.formatted_address: 66 Bhulabhai Desai Road, Breach Candy, Mumbai 400026, India
Breach Candy Swimming & Bath Trust.name: Breach Candy Swimming & Bath Trust
Breach Candy Swimming & Bath Trust.description: The Breach Candy Club is known for its iconic seafront saltwater swimming pool. It also features tennis courts, a fitness center, and dining. Membership is exclusive and highly coveted.

Catholic Gymkhana.formatted_address: 47-A, Netaji Subhash Road, Marine Drive, Mumbai 400002, India
Catholic Gymkhana.name: Catholic Gymkhana
Catholic Gymkhana.description: Founded over a century ago, this club offers indoor sports and social spaces for the Catholic community, located right on Marine Drive.

Celebration Sports Club.formatted_address: Garden No.5, Lokhandwala Complex, Andheri (West), Mumbai 400053, India
Celebration Sports Club.name: Celebration Sports Club
Celebration Sports Club.description: Modern suburban club with extensive sports infrastructure including tennis, squash, cricket, and skating rinks. Offers pool, gym, dining and event spaces.

Chembur Gymkhana.formatted_address: 16th Road, Near Ambedkar Garden, Chembur East, Mumbai 400071, India
Chembur Gymkhana.name: Chembur Gymkhana
Chembur Gymkhana.description: Located in the heart of Chembur, this club provides family-friendly sports facilities and recreational amenities for members.

Cricket Club of India.formatted_address: Brabourne Stadium, Dinshaw Vacha Road, Churchgate, Mumbai 400020, India
Cricket Club of India.name: Cricket Club of India
Cricket Club of India.description: CCI is one of India’s top sporting institutions, featuring the historic Brabourne Stadium. Offers world-class sports, dining, and event venues for elite members.

Dadar Club.formatted_address: Lokmanya Tilak Colony, Lane No.3, Dadar (East), Mumbai 400014, India
Dadar Club.name: Dadar Club
Dadar Club.description: Dadar Club is a modern recreational club offering indoor sports like badminton and table tennis, a gym, and event spaces. It serves as a local hub for fitness and community events.

Ghatkopar Jolly Gymkhana.formatted_address: Kirol Street, Jugaldas Modi Marg, Ghatkopar (West), Mumbai 400086, India
Ghatkopar Jolly Gymkhana.name: Ghatkopar Jolly Gymkhana
Ghatkopar Jolly Gymkhana.description: One of the oldest clubs in the eastern suburbs, it offers a range of sports facilities including tennis courts, swimming pool, indoor games and a health club.

Golden Swan Country Club.formatted_address: Yeoor Hills, Off Pokharan Road No.1, Thane (West) 400606, India
Golden Swan Country Club.name: Golden Swan Country Club
Golden Swan Country Club.description: Set in scenic Yeoor Hills, this 26-acre country club offers a 9-hole golf course, swimming pools, tennis, nature trails and resort-like amenities for leisure and events.

Indus Club.formatted_address: One BKC, A Wing, 4th Floor, Bandra Kurla Complex, Mumbai 400051, India
Indus Club.name: Indus Club
Indus Club.description: An elite members-only business and social club offering a luxury gym, spa, co-working areas, fine dining, and event space. Membership is by invitation only.

Islam Gymkhana.formatted_address: Netaji Subhash Chandra Bose Road, Marine Lines, Mumbai 400002, India
Islam Gymkhana.name: Islam Gymkhana
Islam Gymkhana.description: Islam Gymkhana is a historic seafront club on Marine Drive with a large sports ground used for cricket and football, mainly serving the Muslim community.

Jolie's.name: Jolie's
Jolie's.description: Jolie's is a boutique, members-only club known for luxury experiences, fine dining, elite networking, and wellness facilities including a spa and gym. Invite-only.

Juhu Vile Parle Gymkhana Club.formatted_address: N.S. Road No. 13, JVPD Scheme, Juhu, Mumbai 400049, India
Juhu Vile Parle Gymkhana Club.name: Juhu Vile Parle Gymkhana Club
Juhu Vile Parle Gymkhana Club.description: Founded in 1925, JVPG Club offers a full suite of sports and recreation amenities for members, including swimming, racket sports, dining, and social spaces.

Khar Gymkhana.name: Khar Gymkhana
Khar Gymkhana.description: A legacy suburban club with extensive sports infrastructure including swimming, racket sports, a shooting range, and gym facilities. Popular among Bandra/Khar residents.

Medical College Gymkhana.name: Medical College Gymkhana
Medical College Gymkhana.description: A gymkhana primarily for medical students and staff of Mumbai’s medical colleges. Includes a cricket ground and space for college-level sports and events.

National Sports Club of India (NSCI).formatted_address: Lala Lajpatrai Marg, Royal Western India Turf Club, Mahalakshmi, Mumbai 400018, India
National Sports Club of India (NSCI).name: National Sports Club of India (NSCI)
National Sports Club of India (NSCI).description: NSCI is one of Mumbai’s premier multisport clubs, offering world-class sports courts, a large pool, gym, and its iconic indoor stadium (NSCI Dome) for events.

Navi Mumbai Sports Association.name: Navi Mumbai Sports Association
Navi Mumbai Sports Association.description: NMSA is a large-scale sports complex in Vashi offering an Olympic-sized pool, tennis, badminton, squash, table tennis, gym and frequent competitions and coaching programs.

Parmananddas Jivandas Hindu Gymkhana.formatted_address: Netaji Subhash Road, Marine Drive, Mumbai 400002, India
Parmananddas Jivandas Hindu Gymkhana.name: Parmananddas Jivandas Hindu Gymkhana
Parmananddas Jivandas Hindu Gymkhana.description: One of the oldest community gymkhanas on Marine Drive, with a cricket ground and tennis courts. Membership is primarily community-based, with deep historic roots.

Parsi Gymkhana.formatted_address: Netaji Subhash Road, Marine Drive, Mumbai 400002, India
Parsi Gymkhana.name: Parsi Gymkhana
Parsi Gymkhana.description: Historic seafront club established in 1888 for the Parsi community. Primarily known for its cricket ground, it continues to host matches and community events.

Ripon Club.formatted_address: Mahatma Gandhi Road, Fort, Mumbai 400001, India
Ripon Club.name: Ripon Club
Ripon Club.description: A heritage dining and social club associated with the Parsi community. It offers reading rooms, a dining hall and card room, but minimal sports infrastructure.

Royal Bombay Yacht Club.formatted_address: Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Marg, Apollo Bunder, Colaba, Mumbai 400001, India
Royal Bombay Yacht Club.name: Royal Bombay Yacht Club
Royal Bombay Yacht Club.description: Founded in 1846, RBYC is a prestigious sailing club near the Gateway of India. Offers yacht berths, regattas, dining, and residential rooms for members.

Royal Palms Golf & Country Club.formatted_address: Aarey Milk Colony, Goregaon (East), Mumbai 400065, India
Royal Palms Golf & Country Club.name: Royal Palms Golf & Country Club
Royal Palms Golf & Country Club.description: Luxury country club featuring an 18-hole golf course, pool, clubhouse, and resort-style amenities. A scenic green retreat within city limits.

Royal Western Indian Turf Club.formatted_address: Mahalakshmi Race Course, Mahalaxmi, Mumbai 400034, India
Royal Western Indian Turf Club.name: Royal Western Indian Turf Club
Royal Western Indian Turf Club.description: RWITC manages the Mahalaxmi Racecourse and is the face of thoroughbred horse racing in Mumbai. Offers viewing pavilions, stables, riding and social spaces.

Sher-E-Punjab Gymkhana & Health Club.name: Sher-E-Punjab Gymkhana & Health Club
Sher-E-Punjab Gymkhana & Health Club.description: A community-focused gymkhana offering a pool, gym, and basic sports infrastructure. Also hosts local events, camps, and gatherings in the Andheri East area.

Soho House Mumbai (Soho House Group).formatted_address: Juhu Tara Road, Juhu, Mumbai 400049, India
Soho House Mumbai (Soho House Group).name: Soho House Mumbai (Soho House Group)
Soho House Mumbai (Soho House Group).description: A global private members club for creatives. This Juhu location has a rooftop pool, gym, restaurants, lounges, and curated events. Stylish, exclusive, and artsy.

The A.formatted_address: One India Bulls Center (now One World Center), Tower 2A, 8th Floor, Lower Parel, Mumbai 400013, India
The A.name: The A
The A.description: Previously a members-only social club with wellness and dining. Merged into The Quorum Mumbai in 2021. Featured a gym, Japanese sauna, work and event spaces.

The Club Mumbai.formatted_address: 197, D. N. Nagar, Andheri (West), Mumbai 400053, India
The Club Mumbai.name: The Club Mumbai
The Club Mumbai.description: A large family-oriented suburban club offering tennis courts, jogging track, swimming pool, gym, spa, restaurants, banquet halls, and kids’ play zones.

The Modernist.formatted_address: 33rd Floor, Four Seasons Hotel, 1/136, Dr. E Moses Rd, Worli, Mumbai 400018, India
The Modernist.name: The Modernist
The Modernist.description: An exclusive rooftop club atop Four Seasons Mumbai. Focused on networking, culture and fine dining, not sports. Features lounges, meeting rooms, and curated events.

The Quorum Mumbai.formatted_address: One World Center, Tower 2A, 8th Floor, Senapati Bapat Marg, Lower Parel, Mumbai 400013, India
The Quorum Mumbai.name: The Quorum Mumbai
The Quorum Mumbai.description: Contemporary members club that absorbed The A. Combines co-working, fitness, fine dining, and creative events. Popular among business and creative professionals.

Umbergoan Club.name: Umbergoan Club
Umbergoan Club.description: Weekend getaway club affiliated with Mumbai-based institutions. Offers swimming pool, racket sports, and resort lodging near the Gujarat-Maharashtra coast.

United Services Club.formatted_address: Near Afghan Church, Colaba, Mumbai 400005, India
United Services Club.name: United Services Club
United Services Club.description: Established for armed forces officers and their families. Offers a private 9-hole golf course, pool, tennis/squash courts, sailing options and secure facilities.

Willingdon Catholic Gymkhana.formatted_address: Church Avenue, Santa Cruz (West), Mumbai 400054, India
Willingdon Catholic Gymkhana.name: Willingdon Catholic Gymkhana
Willingdon Catholic Gymkhana.description: Historic community gymkhana with a football ground and indoor sports facilities. Hosts cultural, youth and sporting events for Catholic community members.

Willingdon Sports Club.name: Willingdon Sports Club
Willingdon Sports Club.description: Elite legacy club with an 18-hole golf course, tennis, squash courts, swimming pool, and old-world dining and social spaces. Very selective membership.

Wilson College Gymkhana.name: Wilson College Gymkhana
Wilson College Gymkhana.description: Part of Wilson College, this gymkhana offers cricket and football grounds on Marine Drive for student and inter-collegiate events. Not open to general public.
